snippet.title: "Sister Code" - 2015 (Starring Amber Rose, Eva Marcille and Drew Sidora) Full Movie
snippet.description:
Three foster sisters with very different personalities come together when their mother dies. With her gone, they have to learn how to navigate through love, life and family without her.

Director
Corey Grant

Writers
Randall Hooper
Darien Curry
Don Hale Jr.

Cast
Amber Rose as Lexi
Eva Marcille as Sheila
Drew Sidora as Lavae
Marcus T. Paulk as Lil Danger
Don Hale Jr. as Brian
Anne-Marie Johnson as Mama Layne
Amin Joseph as Thomas
Sade Kimora Young as Young Sheila
Asia Monet Ray as Young Lexi
Laya DeLeon Hayes as Young Lavae
Essence Atkins as Corrine Wells
Erica Ash as Jamaya
Michele Weaver as Sonya
Jason Looney as Tyler
Rolonda Watts as Dr. Riley
Brooklyn McLinn as Rick
Lanett Tachel as Wednesday
Vince Allen as Xen doormam
